        <item>
            <title>1.6.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 23:57:21 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>16</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.6.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Changes
- Modernized status bar design: replaced terminal TUI-style layout with pill badges, thin capsule progress bars, and `.ultraThinMaterial` background
- Model name displayed as short form in a purple badge (e.g. "Opus 4.6" instead of "claude-opus-4-6")
- VCS branch shown in a green badge with emoji prefix
- Center-aligned status bar elements to match webview prompt input
- Hover tooltips on all status bar segments for detailed information

### Bug Fixes
- Fixed appcast delta generation for Sparkle updates
]]></description>
